casebody.data:
BULK JULIANA, LTD., et al., petitioners,
v.
WORLD FUEL SERVICES (SINGAPORE) PTE, LTD. No. 16-26. Supreme Court of the United States June 26, 2017.

Motion of Star Trident II, LLC, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied.
